{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770127920,"nonce":"nIVsgGinRKJw60zyf20/mHJzC7E=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87n8zoi","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/138","origin":"github"},"title":"Bug: `make sync` broken - skips all overlay repos with wrong paths","message":"## Problem\n\n`make sync` is currently broken - it skips all repositories with \"could not resolve repository path\" errors.\n\n## Reproduction\n\n```bash\n$ make sync\nChecking ros2_agent_workspace...\n  🚀 On default branch 'main'. Pulling updates...\n     ✅ Already up to date.\nSkipping camp: could not resolve repository path (tried /home/roland/.../workspaces/ui_ws/src/camp).\nSkipping rqt_marine_radar: could not resolve repository path (tried /home/roland/.../workspaces/ui_ws/src/rqt_marine_radar).\n[... repeated for all 21 overlay repos ...]\n```\n\n**Result**: Root repo syncs, but all overlay repos are skipped.\n\n## Root Cause\n\n`.agent/scripts/sync_repos.py` is hardcoded to look for repositories in `workspaces/*_ws/` but the actual directory structure is `layers/main/*_ws/`.\n\n```python\n# sync_repos.py (line ~XX) - WRONG PATH\nrepo_path = os.path.join(workspace_root, \"workspaces\", f\"{ws_name}_ws\", \"src\", repo_name)\n```\n\nThis path scheme is outdated and doesn't match current workspace layout.\n\n## Impact\n\n- **Severity**: High - Basic sync functionality completely broken\n- **Workaround**: Manual `cd layers/main/*_ws/src \u0026\u0026 vcs pull` in each workspace (6 commands)\n- **Affects**: All users trying to sync repositories via Makefile\n\n## Proposed Fix\n\n**Option 1: Fix sync_repos.py** (maintain Python script)\n- Update paths to use `layers/main/*_ws/` instead of `workspaces/*_ws/`\n- Add path validation to fail fast if workspace doesn't exist\n\n**Option 2: Replace with shell script** (simpler)\n```bash\n# Makefile target\nsync:\n@echo \"Syncing repositories...\"\n@cd $(ROOT_DIR) \u0026\u0026 git pull --ff-only || true\n@for ws in layers/main/*_ws; do \\\necho \"Syncing $$(basename $$ws)...\"; \\\ncd $$ws/src \u0026\u0026 vcs pull; \\\ndone\n```\n\n**Recommendation**: Option 2 (simpler, harder to break)\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- ✅ `make sync` successfully syncs all workspace repositories\n- ✅ No \"could not resolve repository path\" errors\n- ✅ Both root repo and overlay repos are updated\n- ✅ Works in both main workspace and worktrees\n\n## Priority\n\n**High** - Core functionality is broken\n\n## Effort\n\n**Small** (30 minutes)\n\n---\n**🤖 Authored-By**: `Copilot CLI Agent` (Claude Sonnet 4.5)","files":null}]}